  "description": [
    "FOUR FASCISTI HEAD IN VEILED MANNER WARNS ENEMIES Special to The Leader ROME In commemoration of the socalled first year of the Fascist era the supreme council of Fascism issued a grandiloquent proclamation on Aug 4 1923 in which the Catholic and So cialist parties were placed on the proscription list as enemies of Fas cism The proclamation declares that Fascism will achieve its aims at any price In a veiled manner the enemies of Fascism are warned that Mussolini has the power to en force his decrees and that Fascism has demonstrated its ability to endure against all attacks The official proclamation of certain political parties as enemies of Fas cism is a real threat against the lives of the Catholic and Socialist leaders Calls for Victims In fact the listing of the enemies of Fascism is practically a listing of prospective victims Mussolini him self expressed this idea in a telegram to the Fascists of Toscana He ad vised them to save the red hot lead for the enemies of the fatherland and of Fascism Although the new press laws spon sored by Mussolini forbid any in citement to crime or hatred by means of articles commentaries foot"
  ],
